A really good car to drive, the second car I own that can take so many corners flat out, making it ideal for speed zones and road & street races.
The other car I own that is good for the aforementioned speed zones, road races & street races is the Ferrari FXX-K Evo I have from buying it from the Car Pass. Makes earning 20 points during the weekly Festival Playlist really worth it, and let myself experience how fun the Hide and Seek game mode is as the weekly Forzathon challenge requires you to complete a game of Hide and Seek in the Ariel Nomad as the final part of the four parts of the weekly challenge.
